<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٣٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٣٣٨٤ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ فِي الْمَرْأَةِ تَأْتِي الْمَرْأَةَ بِالرَّفْغَةِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«تُجْلَدَانِ، كُلُّ وَاحِدَةٍ مِنْهُمَا مِائَةً»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>